Books Reader - its a perfect e-reading experience. Overdrive your reading skills everyday.

For everyone reader we gift free books and e-reading collections.
Books Reader is a laconic pocket library and intuitive tool for a perfect reading experience. Without extra fluff or complexity, it takes care of all the basic needs: managing your ebook collections, getting the text on the screen and letting you interact with it as you go at your prime reading.
For a start, the app builds a library for you by rounding up all the book files stored on the device. Books Reader works with most popular ebooks formats (epub, fb2, mobi etc.), including zip archives. If necessary, you can tweak the list manually, by adding or removing specific titles for ibooks. 
However big your collection gets, browsing will remain easy thanks to a provided set of filters. Besides, the system is keeping track of your history to display the books in order of relevance. 
Viewing the book, you can adjust the settings for the best effect: change size and color of the text, pick the right theme and brightness level, use various controls options for turning pages. The combination of a progress bar, bookmarking and a search tool help to navigate the text effortlessly. Make sure to select the excerpts that stayed with you and import them to Notes with just a couple of taps.


Books Reader offers:
- A variety of ebook formats (epub, fb2,PDF, mobi and others);
- Auto unpacking of zip archives;
- A smart manager of the books stored on your device;
- Read/unread books tracker;
- Filtering system (by author, by date added or read, etc.);
- Adjustable page/text settings (brightness, size, color, theme and more);
- Several controls methods (scrolling, tapping or using buttons);
- Marking pages and taking notes.

